ales of  billion it now has about  stores in  states with store formats that include grocery and multidepartment stores convenience stores and jewelry stores are you looking for their coupons if yes visit the “saving” category on wwwkrogercom you can find the weekly ad digital coupons and the recent promotions  thoughts on “wwwkrogerfeedbackcom – kroger receipt survey” edwardseptember   at  pmpermalink i have been shopping the kroger at  wgovernment st in brandon ms since it opened i have always been very happy with the service there the last two times i was there i was confronted with a person one inside the store asking for money to pay for her grocery’s  one in the parking asking for money this appears to be the same lady since this store is in a very nice area i don’t understand it i have not seen her around any other of the stores i did report her to personal after being confronted inside the store the store one in the karen whitmoreseptember   at  pmpermalink i did not have enough numbers to fill out the required i’d don’t take up customers time if there’s not proper information on receipt i took time to do it and couldn’t very frustrated thank you bryson w belmont dr sw calhoun ga kellieseptember   at  pmpermalink i have been participating in the kroger feedback surveys for quite some time however my last two receipts from kroger didn’t have a link or code to enter in the survey has something changed i have loved the  extra bonus fuel rewards on my account please bring the survey back melissa hardenburghmarch   at  ampermalink this is the third time i had a receipt from krogers and was unable to fill out the feedback numbers why is this happening why offer this if it is not going to work melissa comments are closed popular surveys burger king receipt survey kfc receipt survey kohls receipt survey subway receipt survey mcdonald’s receipt survey new receipt surveys wwwfeedbackgapfactorycom – gap factory receipt survey wwwjcpenneycomsurvey – jcpenney receipt sur