roger operations fact book careers values about kroger the kroger co nysekr is one of the worlds largest grocery retailers with fiscal  sales of  billion the kroger co family of stores spans many states with store formats that include grocery and multidepartment stores discount convenience stores and jewelry stores we operate under nearly two dozen banners all of which share the same belief in building strong local ties and brand loyalty with our customers  about kroger history of kroger operations fact book careers contact us evidence of insurance stay connected facebook pinterest kroger krogernews news room press releases awards  recognition multimedia library media contacts kroger in the news statements  policies investor relations investor faqs reports  statements webcasts community sustainability bringing hope to the table honoring our heroes sharing courage community rewards kroger foundation vendors  suppliers become a supplier kroger supplier selfregistration supplier diversity merchandise compliance corporate brands vendors the kroger family of companies all comments  copyright  the kroger company all rights reserved terms and conditions  privacy policy  site map the kroger co  operations vendors  suppliers careers contact us search about kroger news room investor relations community sustainability kroger corporate  about kroger  operations about kroger history of kroger operations grocery retail convenience locations fine jewelry manufacturing fact book careers values operations operations overview food stores are our primary business and account for approximately  of total company sales our convenience and jewelry stores and manufacturing facilities contribute the remainder of total sales the information below is current as of june   we operate  grocery retail stores in  states under nearly two dozen banners our formats include supermarkets priceimpact warehouse stores and multidepartment stores which are similar to supercenters but offer an expanded variety of national brand appeal and general merchandise state by state facts can be seen here kroger also operates  convenience stores under six banners in  states our cstores provide valuable synergies for the rapid expansion of our supermarket fuel centers  fine jewelry stores under names like fred meyer jewelers and littman jewelers this is a highmargin business with good cash flow kroger is the only major us supermarket company to operate an economical threetier distribution system kroger also operates  food production or manufacturing facilities producing high quality privatelabel products that provide value for customers and enhanced margins for kroger kroger operates  supermarket fuel centers which are a natural addition to our onestopshopping strategy krogers  pharmacies located in our combination food and drug stores provide high quality services at everyday low prices fy  fy  fy  nd qtr rd qtr th qtr st qtr nd qtr rd qtr th qtr st qtr store count  beginning of quarter         new stores         stores acquired  new         stores acquired  relocations         relocations         subtotal         expansions         subtotal         operational closures         store count  end of quarter         food store square footage  end of quarter millions         remodels         fy  fy  fy  supermarket formats nd qtr rd qtr th qtr st qtr nd qtr rd qtr th qtr st qtr combo stores         marketplace stores         multidepartment stores         priceimpact warehouse stores         total supermarkets         fy  fy  fy  nd qtr rd qtr th qtr st qtr nd qtr rd qtr th qtr st qtr convenience stores         manufacturing plants         jewelry stores         supermarket fuel centers         the little clinic tlc         pharmacies         q     smiths stores coded as marketplace stores were changed to multidepartment stores based on square footage about kroger history of kroger operations fact book careers contact us evidence of insurance stay connected facebook pinterest kroge